metadata.description: This is the NFT artwork collection of BILLETE 1000 PESOS ARGENTINOS instead of official fiat, which is created as one of the fans of Lionel Messi to celebrate Argentinos being the champion of the FIFA World Cup 2022 in Qatar. You could always trade this NFT back with us for 1000 PESOS (before gas fee) in USDT on Ethereum by sending us a messge on Telegram @Messi_Banknote.
metadata.name: Lionel Messi Commemorative Banknote by fans
